data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bed, 2.5-bath home with a bonus room or potential 4th bedroom upstairs. Boasting grand 12-foot ceilings in the living areas, and newly stained hardwoods this residence offers a sense of spaciousness and luxury. The primary bedroom features a vaulted ceiling and ensuite, complete with/ a soaker tub, walk-in shower, dual vanity, and a walk-in closet. The two guest rooms downstairs are on the other side of the house from the primary.  The kitchen is a culinary delight with marble countertops, an electric range, built-in mircowave hood, dishwasher and an adjacent eat-in area all updated in the last 4 years. For more formal occasions, enjoy the elegant formal dining room. The large laundry room, conveniently located off the garage, includes a mud-area for added functionality. The HVAC system is a year old and the roof less than eight years old.  Step outside to the expansive backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The patio provides a picturesque view of the wooded space beyond the fully fenced yard, creating a serene and private atmosphere. This home seamlessly combines style, comfort, and functionality, making it an ideal haven for any homeowner.
